These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, emerald, purple, pink
4 different games are played: scrabble, chess, billiard, go
1. the person playing go is not to the right of the person playing scrabble##8
2. the person playing go is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
3. the person who likes emerald is on the left or right of the person who likes purple##3
4. the person who likes pink is somewhere to the right of the person playing chess##5
5. the person who likes pink is not to the left of the person playing go##8
6. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the left of the person who likes emerald##5
7. the person who likes emerald is somewhere between the person who likes grey and the person playing chess##7
8. the person who likes emerald and the person playing go have the same parity positions##9
9. the person who likes purple and the person playing scrabble have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | grey | emerald | purple     | pink |
| Pet           | billiard   | go     | chess | scrabble  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, fuchsia, ivory, green
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, blend, montecristo, dunhill
1. the bongani-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
2. the dunhill-smoker and the person who likes fuchsia have the same parity positions##9
3. the blend-smoker is not to the right of the montecristo-smoker##8
4. the bongani-smoker is not to the right of the person who likes green##8
5. the bongani-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who likes lavender##5
6. the person who likes lavender is somewhere to the right of the blend-smoker##5
7. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere to the right of the person who likes lavender##5
8. the person who likes green is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | green     | ivory    | lavender | fuchsia    |
| Hobby      | bongani | blend | montecristo      | dunhill |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, animation, time-travel, romance
House: art-deco, victorian, gothic-revival, ranch-style
1. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the left of the gothic-revival house##5
2. the art-deco house is somewhere to the right of the person watching time-travel movies##5
3. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
4. the person watching animation movies is on the far left##1
5. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the art-deco house##1
7. the art-deco house is not to the left of the victorian house##8
8. the person watching animation movies and the victorian house have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | animation    | time-travel   | epic    | romance  |
| Food       | victorian | ranch-style | art-deco | gothic-revival |

