.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, italian, french, thai
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, tea, coffee, cola
1. the person drinking fanta is the italian##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the italian##5
4. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the french##3
5. the person drinking tea is on the left of the colombian##1
6. the thai and the person drinking cola have the same parity positions##9
7. the french is on the left or right of the colombian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | thai | french | colombian  | italian |
| Music-Genre   | coffee             | tea          | cola | fanta    |

