.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, taxi, trike, bike
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, romance, disaster, sports
1. the person driving the trike is not the person watching disaster movies##6
2. the person watching thriller movies and the person driving the car have different parity positions##9
3. the person watching romance movies and the person driving the taxi have different parity positions##9
4. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
6. the person driving the taxi is not the person watching romance movies##6
7. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the taxi##5
8. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person driving the car##1
9. the person watching sports movies is not the person driving the bike##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | car | trike | bike  | taxi |
| Pet           | romance   | thriller     | disaster | sports      |

