4. the fan dubstep and the person drinking cola have the same parity positions##9
5. the person drinking soy-milk and the fan dubstep have different parity positions##9
6. the fan pop is not to the left of the person drinking water##8
7. the fan soul is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
8. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the fan soul##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | lemonade | water | cola | soy-milk |
| Nationality   | soul        | pop    | dubstep   | folk |

