2. the person watching romance movies is not to the right of the person watching action movies##8
3. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
4. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
5. the person traveling to london is not the person watching superhero movies##6
6. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to london##5
7. the person traveling to berlin and the person watching action movies have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
