4 different pets are kept: turtle, horse, mouse, lizard
1. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the owner of the lizard is the person who's sport is rowing##1
4. the owner of the horse and the person who's sport is cricket have different parity positions##9
5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2     |      3       |     4     |
| Food    | rowing | ice-hockey | badminton   | cricket   |
| Hobby   | lizard  | mouse   | horse | turtle |

