.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-12::.
4 different games are played: canasta, scrabble, backgammon, whist
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, daisy, marigold, poppy
1. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
2. the person playing backgammon is not to the left of the person who growspoppy##8
3. the person playing whist and the person who growsdaisy have the same parity positions##9
4. the person who growspoppy is the person playing whist##1
5. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the right of the person who growsiris##5
6. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |   3   |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | scrabble  | whist  | backgammon | canasta    |
| Transport     | marigold | poppy | iris  | daisy |

