2. the analyst is not to the right of the manager##8
3. the owner of the horse is not to the left of the owner of the lizard##8
4. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
5. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the journalist##3
6. the analyst is on the far left##1
7. the manager is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
8. the owner of the rabbit is the writer##1
9. the owner of the lizard and the manager have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | chinchilla   | lizard    | horse | rabbit    |
| Nationality   | analyst | manager | journalist   | writer |

