.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-17::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, guinea-pig, chinchilla, bird
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, mauve, purple, brown
 1. the owner of the guinea-pig and the person who likes purple have the same parity positions##9
 2. the owner of the chinchilla is not to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##8
 3. the person who likes blue is somewhere between the owner of the guinea-pig and the owner of the cat##7
 4. the person who likes purple is somewhere to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##5
 5. the owner of the chinchilla is in an odd position##4
 6. the person who likes purple is not to the left of the owner of the bird##8
 7. the owner of the bird and the person who likes mauve have the same parity positions##9
 8. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the person who likes brown##3
 9. the person who likes brown is in an odd position##4
10. the owner of the bird is not to the right of the person who likes blue##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage      | cat  | bird | chinchilla  | guinea-pig |
| Music-Genre   | brown | purple     | blue | mauve     |

