3. the person who likes lilac is not to the right of the old-henry-smoker##8
4. the person who likes turquise is not to the right of the person who likes emerald##8
5. the old-henry-smoker is in an even position##4
6. the vegafina-smoker and the person who likes light-blue have the same parity positions##9
7. the old-henry-smoker and the person who likes lilac have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1      |   2    |     3      |       4        |
| Job   | light-blue | turquise | emerald | lilac |
| Pet   | vegafina    | montecristo   | pall-mall        | old-henry            |

