.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
House: cottage, tower, farmhouse, victorian
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, roller, helicopter, car
 1. the victorian house is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 3. the person driving the car is not to the right of the person driving the helicopter##8
 4. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is not the tower house##6
 6. the victorian house is not to the right of the cottage house##8
 7. the victorian house and the person driving the roller have the same parity positions##9
 8. the tower house is not to the right of the farmhouse house##8
 9. the victorian house is the person driving the roller##1
10. the tower house and the person driving the roller have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | tower    | farmhouse        | victorian   | cottage      |
| Hobby      | car | helicopter | roller | jet-ski |

 